videos.description: Jalen Hurts puts Alabama on the board with a long touchdown run in the first minute of the game.
videos.headline: Hurts breaks free for 55-yard TD

videos.description: Jalen Hurts connects with Hale Hentges for a 23-yard touchdown to extend Alabama's lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Hurts to Hentges down the middle for a TD

videos.description: Jalen Hurts rushes for a 3-yard touchdown to add to Alabama's lead.
videos.headline: Hurts' 2nd TD run widens Alabama's lead

videos.description: Damien Harris runs five yards for an Alabama touchdown at the end of the second quarter.
videos.headline: Harris for a 5-yard TD

videos.description: Jalen Hurts runs for 16 yards to put the Crimson Tide in field goal range.
videos.headline: Hurts' 16 yard run leads to Alabama field goal

videos.description: Alabama freshman RB Najee Harris rushes for  25 yards for a Crimson Tide first down.
videos.headline: Freshman Harris gets longest run of career

videos.description: Anthony Averett's intercepts Chason Virgil's pass and returns it 30 yards, which leads to a Crimson Tide field goal.
videos.headline: Averett's first career pick puts Alabama in red zone

videos.description: Chason Virgil completes to Derrion Grim for a 26-yard touchdown in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Virgil to Grim TD closes gap on Alabama

videos.description: Tua Tagovailoa connects with Henry Ruggs III for a 16-yard TD late fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Ruggs III further extends the lead with a TD

videos.description: Alabama head coach Nick Saban discusses the improvements his team still needs to make after their 41-10 win over Fresno State.
videos.headline: Saban: Alabama 'nickled and dimed' on defense

videos.description: Anthony Becht and Adam Amin highlight Jalen Hurts and the rest of the Crimson Tide in their success in the 41-10 win over Fresno State.
videos.headline: Becht and Amin recap Alabama win

videos.description: Jalen Hurts rushes for 154 yards and two touchdowns and throws a touchdown pass in No. 1 Alabama's 41-10 win over Fresno State.
videos.headline: Alabama rolls over Fresno State

videos.description: After Alabama's 41-10 victory over Fresno State, Nick Saban was asked to evaluate the power of the offensive line but he quickly turns the question back on the media.
